sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Agent console (UI)
    participant CG as ClientsGateway
    participant Stats as StatisticsService
    participant Remote as Remote agent-manager socket
    participant AG as AgentsGateway
    participant Prov as Agent provider

    Note over UI,Prov: Prompt enhancement — isolated from main chat transcript

    UI->>CG: forward { event: enhanceChat, agentId, payload }
    CG->>Stats: recordChatInput (draft, interaction_kind: prompt_enhancement)
    CG->>Remote: enhanceChat payload
    Remote->>AG: enhanceChat
    AG->>Prov: sendMessage (continue false, resumeSessionSuffix for Cursor)
    Prov-->>AG: model text
    AG-->>Remote: chatEnhanceResult (unicast to initiating socket only)
    Remote-->>CG: chatEnhanceResult
    CG->>Stats: recordChatOutput (enhanced text or failure)
    CG-->>UI: forward chatEnhanceResult to client

    Note over UI: Updates textarea only - no chat bubbles / no agent_messages
